          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-weight=bold font-size=20px> Community Voices: Solitary Refinement </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-size=12px height=15px font-weight=bold> Alex Cheng ’23, Staff Writer </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#637381 font-size=16px> Community Voices is a section started and run by the Features section that gives community members the opportunity to submit personal vlogs, blogs, journal entries, poems, etc., relating to their lives off of the main campus.  </mj-text>
