          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-weight=bold font-size=20px> Community Voices: Alone in Community </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-size=12px height=15px font-weight=bold> Ben Weiss ’21, Contributing Writer </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#637381 font-size=16px> "Alone in Community" is an essay written by Ben Weiss ’21 as part of his independent study, Seeking the Better Path for the Hotchkiss Community. An abstract of the essay is included below. Readers can also access the full essay by clicking on the link below. </mj-text>
