          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-weight=bold font-size=20px> Varsity Teams Inspire Motivation Through At-Home Initiatives </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-size=12px height=15px font-weight=bold> Phil Warren ’23, Contributing Writer </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#637381 font-size=16px> Despite school cancellations and social-distancing measures, sports teams are still finding ways to strengthen the bond between team members and train during this pandemic. While it’s impossible to replicate the experience of a season on campus
            with teammates, teams have been trying to keep their players practicing and in shape. </mj-text>
